{
  "stem": "2165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing that the sons used to work for German-- for the border police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they used to give him home certain pieces meat what they used to slaughter, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my uncle wouldn't touch it, because he was strictly kosher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you know, we used to-- we used to help out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So me and my sister had a little bit of merchandise.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Whatever you could, you used to sell and try to survive, that was-- you did whatever you could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the only thing you could go is-- I saw some people collecting poison ivy and cook it and eat it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were Jewish people walking around swollen from hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, in ghetto, there was no-- no possibilities to steal-- from whom?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From you to you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, there was nothing left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I never went out from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Never snuck out from the ghetto, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the Judenfrei broke out, we went into the underground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, in-- in the basement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we prepared rain water outside from the rain, from the gutters in liters.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once a week, Saturday night, they used to open up the bricks-- there's an opening-- go out and bring in as much water as you could.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every week to get the water, right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Otherwise, I stayed in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my sister was taken to a labor camp in Brody, and she worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, a lot of the people who worked in the camp knew where Jews were hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The German used to use them to clean up the furniture and all the wealth of the Jews in the houses and put it in-- in a certain place in Brody.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
